                        <interp inst="t18600611-name-336" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MARY EARLE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>). I lost some coins like these. <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18600611-563-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
